<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-C305C108-02DB-421B-82F7-0B7AD5D9910A" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-C305C108-02DB-421B-82F7-0B7AD5D9910A" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">11 Software upgrade using a USB key</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="M148553-B105"><p class="- topic/p ">This type of upgrade procedure is intended for the service technician and not for a customer. 
</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-610BC863-F7A5-476F-BDAB-783E9B196A7B" type="important"><p class="- topic/p "> NEVER combine multiple of the actions below at once: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">(Clean) installation of the system software 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Replace the Windows controller 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Replace DRC PBA (21PBA04) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Install used Printheads 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "> After each change of a topic listed above a system start-up/reboot must be executed to safeguard settings persistence. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Ignoring this, will result in the need for a restore action and involvement of Service and Support CPP is required. 
</p></note></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-AAF0EDF0-5E7D-4CE7-A0E6-48FF181DB533" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><table id="GUID-6023F88A-C308-48CF-A955-0D834FB8F4AD" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remark 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Create an installation USB key by means of the CreateUSB tool with the option '<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">keep settings</b>'. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> 
<xref keyref="DownloadAndPrepareUSBkeyinstallation" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-BBED23FE-4C3C-4B89-B9AA-CBF2EAFBB049.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>11 Download and prepare the software packages for a USB key installation</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="INSTCON0003" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-A692F06D-10A9-4160-8CBC-E345ED636C31.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>11 How to install the CreateUSB tool</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="20INST-USBKEY" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-51DC0123-5924-4D7D-B345-F3B06B4B248C.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>11 How to create an installation USB Key</xref> 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the customers network cable of the printer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This prevents that an external application to disturb the upgrade process. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Restart the system in order to have an up-to-date back-up on the controller. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><note id="GUID-8D9AA349-C44E-4F2F-AF71-E1C971C4CB37" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">It is not required to wait until the printer is warm. Proceed with the next step as soon as the printer starts initializing. 
</p></note></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Insert the USB key and restart the printer. 
</p><note id="GUID-87754CA8-FB0A-42A0-82ED-0FE621F149E4" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">It is not required to wait until the printer is warm. The restart can be initiated when the printer starts warming-up. 
</p></note><p class="- topic/p ">The installation starts automatically. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Required time: 45 minutes. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">USB verification pop-ups are shown and a progress indication is shown during the installation. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The installation is finished when the system is in stand-by. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">During the start-up the system version number is shown. 
</p><note id="GUID-0DE4A294-B8DF-4C01-9839-FF0776715E7D" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> If a clean install is performed (Without "Keep jobs and settings") the system needs to be restarted manually after the installation is finished (Black User Interface-panel and power-button is led Green). 
</p></note></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the USB key from the system. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Re-connect the customers network cable to the printer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if all the system settings are still correct. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Also check that Remote Service is still working if it is used. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="ORSSETUP001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-07BC7664-5AAE-4C27-A331-C2F6D4AB2349.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>How to set up On Remote Service (ORS)</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check in the specific software upgrade procedure if additional actions are required after the software upgrade. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Create an ADAM visit for this upgrade. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="Start_adam" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-685E6504-D43E-4063-96D4-B0A4F752A1F6.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>How to start ADAM</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Optional: Update the RIP driver. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-724C7F1C-09E3-4D8F-B77B-2B159E768314.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>